{"tid":1045352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斥四川美院教授葉永青抄襲三十年　獲利百萬　比利時藝術家籲杯葛","createTime":"2019-03-03T14:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T00:55:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2b64d3928dfb2ceed6730f9c1a158dcd709b94db","tid":1045352,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/yip-01_DLZDh20copy_VnmI7_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fyip-01_DLZDh20copy_VnmI7_1200x0.png&h=87198ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n「有一天，我收到畫廊來電，說見到一批我的作品質素未如理想。我一看，心想：一定是出了些問題。」比利時藝術家 Christian Silvain 說，但當時他大概沒有想到問題竟是這麼嚴重吧？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n自 1980 年代起，Christian Silvain 創作一系列拼湊為題的作品，構圖素材包括鳥、鳥巢，鳥籠、紅色十字架、飛機等。查找之下，他發現有一名藝術家自 1990 年代起「抄考」其作三十年，更憑此在藝術市場獲利數百萬――這名藝術家來自中國，是與畫家張曉剛等人齊名的四川美術學院教授葉永青。<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChristian Silvain 上月接受比利時傳媒《HLN》訪問，指荷蘭阿姆斯特丹一間畫廊東主致電，稱在一場中國藝術的展覽中，發現一幅極似其風格、惟質素未如理想的作品。其代理畫廊 Galerie Jos Depypere 立即進行資料搜集，發現葉永青在 Silvain 開始拼貼創作之後六年，推出風格相近的作品，並於蘇富比、佳士得以數十萬歐元的標價成交。畫廊搜集的資料更顯示，葉永青不單涉嫌抄襲 Silvain，亦曾一度抄襲另一比利時藝術家 Pierre Alechinsky 的風格。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n看過葉永青的作品之後，Silvain 形容取材十分相似，「但人家現在是中國重要的藝術家，還要是策展人，在中國有巨大影響力。把事件說出來，猶如與他對著幹，恐怕一點也不容易。」再考慮到採取法律行動可能耗費大筆金錢，訴訟成果亦未必一定對自己有利，故 Silvain 呼籲歐洲業界予以杯葛。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n面對來自比利時的指控，葉永青本周三回覆《南方都市報》查詢，指「正在爭取與這位藝術家聯繫」。他承認 Christian Silvain 是「對我影響至深的一位藝術家」，但對於記者提出的其他問題，一概暫不回應。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/3_WpOFt_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F3_WpOFt_1200x0.png&h=5af43282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n其他相似作品：葉永青(左)、Christian Silvain(右)，網絡片段截圖<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/1_1Zb31_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F1_1Zb31_1200x0.png&h=67fde57e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n其他相似作品：葉永青(左)、Christian Silvain(右)，網絡片段截圖<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/2_POToo_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F2_POToo_1200x0.png&h=f883bb62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n其他相似作品：葉永青(左)、Christian Silvain(右)，網絡片段截圖"},{"pid":"8003be825ceb9dca532b8542702da35b0a7fab0b","tid":1045352,"uid":37666,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"符合國情"},{"pid":"2e5f33369bc50845a4f013c417b8897ab40f0a7f","tid":1045352,"uid":11148,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"叫親永青都係大仆街黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4f26d56bdb5e135b4c4cb7ad7eef268d983704","tid":1045352,"uid":224533,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"大陸未告返原創轉頭已經算係咁"},{"pid":"57c097e15d169ee0c43134246f14cf3b4aae2dad","tid":1045352,"uid":31920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:22:32.000Z","msg":"唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f1d644e9f1974712ca3b630fea44f216f7cbb3","tid":1045352,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"華人賤種學咩人做藝術家"},{"pid":"f95a92a9a9b05916d244d7a12b3bb88b7bf7070b","tid":1045352,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"又抄"},{"pid":"cba03f027867c967d9431813c6bc4af9910b9fb6","tid":1045352,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"呢個國家由上至下有抄襲DNA"},{"pid":"9102fe8be38c12a99f73dd3e3eb3f3d9b36202db","tid":1045352,"uid":3457,"like":2,"dislike":1,"s